description: eneloop C size spacers allow for eneloop AA batteries to be inserted and utilized in C size battery applications. The battery cells maintain their original eneloop AA cell performance characteristics including 2000mAh, 1500 recharges, and will hold 75 percent of the charge for up to 3 years (when not in use). These adapters are a great alternative when C size batteries are not available. Battery life (per recharge) will vary based on the application. eneloop spacers can be recharged over and over again (up to 1500 times) and are convenient and easy to use. Simply insert a charged eneloop AA battery cell into the "C" size spacer. Once the AA cell in inserted into the spacer it is ready to be used in the device.
title: eneloop SEC-CSPACER4PK C Size Spacers for use with AA battery cells
